    titleEn: 'Carrying the torch: How Ukrainian Baptist Convention upholds a legacy of activism',
    titleUk: 'Презентація Української Навчальної Біблії',
    excerptEn: 'At the height of the Cold War, the Ukrainian diaspora played an active role in influencing public opinion regarding the Soviet Union. What is seldom mentioned is the role that Ukrainian evangelicals played in this period.',
